name: Employees / Bearings, gears, gearing & driving elements - Ireland
description: United Nations Industrial Development Organization (UNIDO). INDSTAT4-Rev.3 contains time series data on five selected data items for the period covering 2005 - 2009. The data are arranged at the 3- and 4-digit level of ISIC (Revision 3) pertaining to the manufacturing sector, which comprises 151 manufacturing categories.
